{"tid":1174784,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[小日本又殺人]  日本神奈川暴徒隨機砍殺小學女童  .........","createTime":"2019-05-28T05:48:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T13:07:37.000Z","uid":150609,"like":2,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"3c5ec4124aa843c07239b6bb5091b7fb067549e0","tid":1174784,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T05:48:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nJ6twf0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnJ6twf0.jpg&h=9ee41edb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZmfaKA5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZmfaKA5.jpg&h=ddf629e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aje62ot.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faje62ot.png&h=bab577bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tWw9fJu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtWw9fJu.jpg&h=a284c617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  &ldquo;這個世界上的一切，早已經掌握在無數只手中，我們看得見、想得到的東西，都已經有了主人，想要!就只有從別人的手里搶!只有踏著染滿了鮮血的階梯，未來才有保証。<br />\n<br />\n永遠用蔑視的眼光去看自己的對手!不論他們什麼身分利刃總會割下他們的頭顱!做為勝利者!我們有資格也有必要徹底的毀滅對方!<br />\n<br />\n讓敵人的鮮血，成為我們的汽油；讓敵人的血肉，成為我們的食物；讓敵人的靈魂，成為我們無盡的勇氣之源；用敵人的生命換來我們強大不可摧毀的力量！<br />\n<br />\n放手大幹一場吧!這是個收割生命的年代!<br />\n<br />\n嗜血!<br />\n<br />\n這一次誰也阻止不了我!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aywAVLV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaywAVLV.jpg&h=21fcfee2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d901dd1a2242ad072dc2dc66acbfc2a6f30a09c","tid":1174784,"uid":52652,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T05:49:25.000Z","msg":"痴撚線蘿莉都斬=.="},{"pid":"6f632c0cb66c1945804330f6e177c39e0f66ba1a","tid":1174784,"uid":232687,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T05:50:11.000Z","msg":"點解個世界會變成咁"},{"pid":"25b1339e782f1561bd8636471d7b6f64fd64a963","tid":1174784,"uid":230235,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T05:51:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"136bfc12cc103ea6c42db8a06dc2b11507566ca0","tid":1174784,"uid":25754,"like":5,"dislike":20,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T05:53:32.000Z","msg":"原來中國真係安全好多-﹏-"},{"pid":"c698dd15a00cb876ff0dadf0206fb63a248b6ad0","tid":1174784,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T05:57:58.000Z","msg":"日本媒體報導，日本時間早上7時44分，神奈川縣川崎市發生殺人事件。民眾報案，登戸第一公園有四名小學生被刺傷，根據警方說法，現場約有16名大人及學童被刺，已有2大人1小孩無呼吸心跳。<br />\n<br />\n現場逮捕一名男子，兇嫌於行兇後試圖割喉自殺，也受了重傷。據指出，現場發現2把菜刀。當時為上班上學的通勤時間，案發現場離小田急線的登戶車站只有200公尺。<br />\n<br />\nNHK 報導，年約50多歲的兇嫌是揮刀刺向在等公車的人，據傳他本人自殘後也無呼吸心跳。"},{"pid":"4023cdf9a4a57ab1d4174d541c82730a96d24d4d","tid":1174784,"uid":106426,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T05:59:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dcaa0ce429371aca01b24d76fbdac7f88e642055","tid":1174784,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T06:01:03.000Z","msg":"關動物咩事。。"},{"pid":"2b6d343b3d6c48003c32e2b1e479e7c83d476f6d","tid":1174784,"uid":150609,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4023cdf9a4a57ab1d4174d541c82730a96d24d4d","tid":1174784,"uid":106426,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T05:59:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T06:01:04.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n<br />\n肯定係假<br />\n<br />\n就算係真都係日本支那人殺 一定係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0142f3edc15d463cd3dde0a4eb6cd0df5bcdee85","tid":1174784,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T06:01:09.000Z","msg":"最後張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b7cc00f93ca2990b65ee6685c1d5387cffb201b","tid":1174784,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T06:01:45.000Z","msg":"無差別殺人事件"},